  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But she was not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, of course, she suggested to me that maybe I didn't know anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had absolutely no, at that time, knowledge or contact with Soviet Union and Bolshevism and communism or something like that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I agreed to her-- with her, maybe that was a good idea to-- to look for the Russian partisans.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- and through my connections, I found out that there is a group of people, Polish people in Warsaw, who were running a business in-- in this territories, the eastern part of Poland territories-- well, of course, German territories, occupied-- German occupied territories.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Apparently, there was a-- a company, and this-- this chief of this company or-- or president of the company was recruiting Polish crafters, like carpenters and-- and-- and smiths, locks, and so on, to go to that place-- apparently there was a city, Dubno in Polish, former Polish Yolhynia region-- and to work-- actually, it was to do maintenance for the German army.",
      "word_count": 67
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The-- every-- you know, almost every small-- even small city, there were some-- some German army units.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And apparently, in this city, Dubno, there were larger German group of troops.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were-- they were stationing there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they needed some kind of maintenance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they used the Polish workers to do the repairs in-- in their quarters and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So this company was looking for-- for somebody who could be a-- a manager of that group.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I wanted to go there.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
